Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I published the full story of the trade that lost me 31 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This was the trade that told me my 90% win rate was fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wrote it down — all the numbers, the full timeline, no sweetening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I thought it would be the coldest piece of content I'd post all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Instead it became the one that sparked the most conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know how much a losing trade is worth if you're willing to write it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}More than ten winning ones you never bothered to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Losing stories teach people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Winning stories just entertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 12 tomorrow — I rebuilt every agent I'd put on a schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
